}\ndistortion, we find no energetically favorable d-wave solution with an overall\nzero chirality within the restriction of the t-J model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jul 2014 19:38:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Sep 2014 08:04:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-23"}
