 low power consumption and radiation-hard\ncomponents making it viable for future space-based millimeter telescopes such\nas the LiteBIRD satellite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jul 2014 13:52:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
